anted garden restaurant, hong kong picture:";i:3;s:64:"Indulge in a sumptuous buffet overgrown with victorian elegance.";i:4;s:87:"The theme of the hotel is of a victorian style, and is located near disneyland harbour.";i:5;s:74:"Enchanted garden is a buffet restaurant at the hong kong disneyland hotel.";i:6;s:130:"Hong kong disneyland hotel is the second disney hotel in the hong kong disneyland resort in penny's bay, lantau island, hong kong.";i:7;s:51:"Mickey de retour à l’hong kong disneyland hotel.";i:8;s:146:"From april 30 to may 3, 2020, the enchanted garden restaurant at the hong kong disneyland hotel will offer “all you can eat” lunch and dinner.";i:9;s:70:"And most of all, you have some of the disney characters as your hosts!";i:10;s:101:"A buffet style restaurant, is open for breakfast and dinner daily and lunch on weekends and holidays.";i:11;s:38:"Hong kong disneyland hotel, hong kong.";i:12;s:73:"This update comes courtesy of our friends at disney magical kingdom blog.";i:13;s:108:"Enchanted garden restaurant is located down a flight of stairs from the lobby at hong kong disneyland hotel.";i:14;s:100:"The enchanted garden restaurant is located inside the hong kong disneyland hotel on the lower level.";i:15;s:69:"The hotel is built on reclaimed land and opened on 12 september 2005.";i:16;s:59:"Signature dishes include 甜品, 自助餐, dinner buffet,.";i:17;s:23:"We are waiting for you!";i:18;s:48:"Enchanted garden restaurant at disneyland hotel.";i:19;s:88:"It is a character dining buffet restaurant that is open for breakfast, lunch and dinner.";i:20;s:53:"The hong kong disneyland hotel itself was impeccable!";i:21;s:95:"Guests will be able to enjoy lunch from 12:00 pm to 4:00 pm or dinner from 6:00 pm to 10:00 pm.";i:22;s:79:"Secondly, we started the day with a splendid breakfast at the enchanted garden.";i:23;s:108:"翠樂庭餐廳enchanted garden restaurant's menu, located at 1/f, hong kong disneyland hotel lantau island.";i:24;s:69:"Mickey mouse | hong kong disneyland hotel enchanted garden restaurant";i:25;s:41:"Low prices, excellent and prompt service.";i:26;s:43:"Location in the hong kong disneyland hotel.";i:27;s:39:"Enchanted garden restaurant, hong kong:";i:28;s:180:"翠樂庭餐廳enchanted garden restaurant's address, online booking, telephone number, ratings, reviews, photos and menu, located at 1/f, hong kong disneyland hotel lantau island.";i:29;s:77:"Les clients pourront déjeuner de 12h00 à 16h00 ou dîner de 18h00 à 22h00.";i:30;s:111:"I guess the main reason is that we managed to recover from the exhaustion of waking up at 4am on our first day!";i:31;s:112:"Hong kong disneyland resort, disneyland hotel, lantau island, hong kong, china (new territories) +852 3510 6000.";i:32;s:138:"See 366 unbiased reviews of enchanted garden restaurant, rated 4.5 of 5 on tripadvisor and ranked #116 of 13,839 restaurants in hong kong.";i:33;s:92:"Reservations accepted, character dining, family style, fine/signature dining, table service.";i:34;s:170:"See 2,626 traveller reviews, 3,645 candid photos, and great deals for hong kong disneyland hotel, ranked #52 of 783 hotels in hong kong and rated 4.5 of 5 at tripadvisor.";i:35;s:123:"Choose from a variety of american and asian favorites, as well as specialty items unique to the hong kong disneyland hotel.";i:36;s:178:"Lihat 367 ulasan objektif tentang enchanted garden restaurant, yang diberi peringkat 4,5 dari 5 di tripadvisor dan yang diberi peringkat no.129 dari 14.474 restoran di hong kong.";i:37;s:130:"This news comes several weeks after character dining resumed at shanghai disneyland, one of the first disney theme parks to close.";i:38;s:73:"Reserve a table at enchanted garden restaurant, hong kong on tripadvisor:";i:39;s:90:"Come to hong kong disneyland and enjoy the luxurious and elegant accommodation experience!";i:40;s:153:"Enchanted garden is one of four food and beverage outlets at the hong kong disneyland hotel, which is located near hong kong disneyland on lantau island.";i:41;s:54:"Lunch and dinner are available, but if not staying at.";i:42;s:77:"Reservations are available, so make sure to book your reservation in advance.";i:43;s:85:"This is where you have your dream disney breakfast at the hong kong disneyland hotel.";i:44;s:144:"According to hong kong disneyland’s website, reservations are now available for enchanted garden restaurant at the hong kong disneyland hotel.";i:45;s:340:"Enchanted garden disneyland hotel 香港 • enchanted garden hong kong disneyland hotel 香港 • enchanted garden restaurant 香港 • enchanted garden restaurant 翠樂庭餐廳 香港 • enchanted garden 翠樂庭餐廳 香港 • enchanted garden, hong kong disneyland hotel 香港 • enchanted garden restaurant penny's bay 香港";i:46;s:76:"Day two of our hong kong disneyland experience was even better than day one.";i:47;s:136:"It also happens to be right next door to bibbidi bobbidi boutique, where girls can dress up like princesses, minnie mouse or tinkerbell.";i:48;s:81:"Guest may enjoy dining credit of hk$400 (“dining credit”) per room per night.";i:49;s:138:"See 367 unbiased reviews of enchanted garden restaurant, rated 4.5 of 5 on tripadvisor and ranked #126 of 14,261 restaurants in hong kong.";i:50;s:120:"They will be offering an “all you can eat” lunch from 12:00pm to 4:00pm or dinner from 6:00pm to 10:00pm from april.";i:51;s:140:"Hong kong disneyland resort offers amazing accommodation options for guests from all over the world, and each hotel has a distinctive theme.";i:52;s:297:"Indoor and outdoor pools, jacuzzis, hot and dry saunas, a full gym, a spa, lots of photo opportunity settings, a garden maze, yummy restaurants and of course, lots of perks like hotel visits from the disney princesses and from the disney stars like mickey mouse, daisy duck, goofy, pluto and more!";i:53;s:57:"An 10% gratuity charge will apply to all delivery orders.";i:54;s:120:"I showed up at 7:30 to find a long line of guests, but the restaurant was vast enough to hold several times this number.";i:55;s:193:"The official hong kong disneyland website has announced that the hong kong disneyland hotel’s enchanted garden restaurant is resuming character dining from today, april 30th, through may 3rd.";i:56;s:140:"And can be made up to 42 days prior to your visit—or 120 days prior to your arrival date if you are staying at hong kong disneyland hotel.";i:57;s:147:"Beside enjoying the elegant decor of the enchanted garden restaurant, you have the most fabulous international buffet, as far as your eyes can see.";i:58;s:101:"The enchanted garden restaurant character breakfast has two sittings, 7:30 to 9:00 and 9:30 to 11:00.";}}